Fully qualified* applicants will receive their first full month free when signing a 13 month or longer lease. <br>
Use that free month to help offset your moving expenses, or purchase new furniture or electronics, or whatever you wish.<br>
<br>
This convenient 2 bedroom apartment features central AC, granite counters, updated appliances, and washer/dryer hookups in a charming garden-style apartments complex.<br>
<br>
Be near the historic Riverfront, Fast Eddies, shopping on Homer Adams, the Lock and Dam, Riverfront hiking/biking trail and other natural parks.<br>
Resident pays electric and gas. Landlord provides water, sewer, and trash.<br>
<br>
Deposit down to secure the apartment is just $420.<br>
<br>
*Fully qualified applicants will make atleast 3x the rental rate in income each month ($2,040+), have no felonies or violent crime convictions, have no evictions or landlord collections, have good credit, and have atleast 12 months of work and rental history. <br>
<i>Applicants that meet most, but not all, of the above requirements may bring on a familial cosigner/guarantor with the Landlord's permission.</i>
